istory Highlights in N.C. State History]. Retrieved 2015-Oct-9.</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" |Conference finish<ref>[http://sidearm.sites.s3.amazonaws.com/gopack.com/documents/2015/8/18/2_Yearly_Records.pdf?id=11686 N.C. State Yearly Records]. Retrieved 2015-Oct-9</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" |Division finish\n! scope=\"col\" |Wins\n! scope=\"col\" |Losses\n! scope=\"col\" |Ties\n! scope=\"col\" |Bowl result<ref>[http://www.collegefootballpoll.com/bowl_history_north_carolina_st.html Bowl History of N.C. State]. Retrieved 2015-Oct-9.</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" |[[AP Poll]]<ref>[http://sidearm.sites.s3.amazonaws.com/gopack.com/documents/2015/8/18/3_Pack_in_AP_Poll.pdf?id=11670 Wolfpack in the AP Poll]. Retrieved 2015-Oct-9.</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" |[[Coaches' Poll]]<ref>[http://www.collegefootballpoll.com/polls_1936_present_i.html College Football Poll History]. Retrieved 2015-Oct-10.</ref>\n|-\n|[[1892 North Carolina A&M Aggies football team|1892]]\n|{{Sortname|Perrin|Busbee}}\n| rowspan=30|Independent\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|01|1}}\n|{{sort|00|0}}\n|{{sort|00|0}}\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|-\n|[[1893 North Carolina A&M Aggies football team|1893]]\n| rowspan=3|{{Sortname|Bart|Gatling}}\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|02|2}}\n|{{sort|00|0}}\n|{{sort|00|0}}\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|-\n|[[1894 North Carolina A&M Aggies football team|1894]]\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|00|0}}\n|{{sort|02|2}}\n|{{sort|00|0}}\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|-\n|[[1895 North Carolina A&M Aggies football team|1895]]\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|01|1}}\n|{{sort|02|2}}\n|{{sort|01|1}}\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|-\n|[[1896 North Carolina A&M Aggies football team|1896]]\n| rowspan=2|{{Sortname|Perrin|Busbee}}\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|01|1}}\n|{{sort|00|0}}\n|{{sort|00|0}}\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|{{sort|-000|N/A}}\n|-\n|[[1897 North Carolina A&M Aggies football team|1897]]\n|\u2014\n|\u2014\n|{{sort|01|1}}\n|{{sort|02|