-shukla-be-seen-show-190312|title=Pearl V Puri and Siddharth Shukla to be seen on THIS show|last=Team|first=Tellychakkar|website=Tellychakkar.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-10}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Khatra Khatra Khatra]]''\n|Guest\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/pearl-v-puri-aparna-dixit-and-ishita-dutta-be-seen-khatra-khatra-khatra-190528|title=Pearl V Puri, Aparna Dixit, and Ishita Dutta to be seen on Khatra Khatra Khatra|last=Team|first=Tellychakkar|website=Tellychakkar.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-10}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Dance Deewane]]''\n|Ganpati Special Episode\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/sidharth-jasmin-pearl-and-surbhi-be-part-of-dance-deewane-s-ganpati-special-190824|title=Sidharth, Jasmin, Pearl, and Surbhi to be a part of Dance Deewane\u2019s Ganpati special|last=Team|first=Tellychakkar|website=Tellychakkar.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-10}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Ace of Space 2|Ace Of Space 2]]''\n|Guest\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/pearl-v-puri-enters-ace-of-space-shares-his-favourite-moment-the-shoot-191015|title=Pearl V Puri enters Ace Of Space; shares his FAVOURITE MOMENT from the shoot!|last=Team|first=Tellychakkar|website=Tellychakkar.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-10}}</ref>\n|-\n|''Wakhra Swag 2020''\n|Himself\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bizasialive.com/colors-announces-new-years-special-show-wakhra-swag/|title=Colors announces New Year's special show 'Wakhra Swag'|last=Baddhan|first=Raj|date=2019-12-30|website=BizAsia {{!}} Media, Entertainment, Showbiz, Brit, Events and Music|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-01-10}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 13)|Bigg Boss 13]]''\n|Guest\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/bigg-boss-13-welcome-all-the-lead-actors-of-colors-primetime-shows-new-year-celebrations|title=Bigg Boss 13 to welcome all the lead actors of Colors' primetime shows for New Year celebrations!|