uri, Pearl V}} \n\n\n[[Category:Living people]] \n[[Category:Indian male models]] \n[[Category:21st-century Indian male actors]] \n[[Category:Indian male soap opera actors]] \n[[Category:People from Agra]] \n[[Category:Male actors in Hindi television]] \n[[Category:Indian male television actors]]  \n[[Category:1989 births]]\n", "name_user": "Pawan Agrawal again", "label": "safe", "comment": "Add his another occupation", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pearl_V_Puri"}
